-- 
Suzuki to Sell Plug-in Hybrid Vehicles in 2013, Nikkei Reports

-- B y   J a e   H u r
-- 
2011-06-12T03:48:14Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-12/suzuki-to-sell-plug-in-hybrid-vehicles-in-2013-nikkei-reports.html
Suzuki Motor Corp. (7269)  plans to begin
selling plug-in hybrid vehicles in 2013, the Nikkei newspaper
reported, without saying where it obtained the information.  The company will base the cars on its Swift models and will
initially sell several thousand units on the domestic market at
prices below 2 million yen ($24,972), the newspaper said today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jae Hur in Tokyo at 
 jhur1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Paul Tighe at 
 ptighe@bloomberg.net  